User Story

As a client looking for a loan.

    I want a clean and firm website for applying to loans so that I can interfere without difficulties.
    I want to see loan calculator before submitting for a loan so that I can calculate my online loan annual payment including percentages.
    I want to see after submitting my score so that I can know for the future submition.
    I want to see which banks are able to provide a loan based on the score so that I can choose between them.
    i want to receive a message or notification regarding my submission so that I can be sure that it was processed correctly. 
